    "accepted path must not accept key material or custody material",
    "accepted path must verify signature before mutation",
    "accepted path must validate balance, nonce, fee, expiry, duplicate pending state, and addresses before mutation",
    "accepted path must append exactly one pending transaction to the local pending file",
    "accepted path must not change chain state",
    "accepted path must write an audit event before reporting success",
    "accepted path must be covered by local smoke before UI mutation controls are considered"
